# Enterprise Knowledge Base — Complete Walkthrough

## Summary
Built a production-ready enterprise knowledge-base platform (formerly Antigravity, now **Enterprise Knowledge Platform**) with 14 pre-loaded Copilot Adoption pages, RBAC, audit logging, security hardening, and deployment configs.

In **Phase 4**, we completely overhauled the UI/UX from a dark theme to a clean, white "Enterprise" theme with a blue sidebar (Moon Base aesthetic) and colorful metric cards.

## Application Running ✅

**Backend:** http://localhost:4000 (NestJS, 7 modules, 30+ routes)
**Frontend:** http://localhost:3000 (Next.js 14, 10 routes)
**Database:** PostgreSQL 16 on port 5433 (Docker: `kb-postgres`)

